title: Trump: I'd 'get along very well with' Putin - KXLY-TV Spokane
text:
There are 1 comment on the KXLY-TV Spokane story from 23 hrs ago, titled Trump: I'd 'get along very well with' Putin . In it, KXLY-TV Spokane reports that:
Donald Trump says he and Russian President Vladimir Putin are "very different" -- but the two share at least a couple of bonds. Namely: They both dislike President Barack Obama.
